History
=======

0.3.0 (2018-12-13)
------------------
* Provide bindings to iblines through gpib.lines and Gpib.lines


0.2.1 (2018-11-28)
------------------

* Fix gpib.ibfind string marshalling


0.2.0 (2018-11-27)
------------------

* Safe cleanup using Gpib.close()


0.1.1 (2018-11-27)
------------------

* Bugfix release


0.1.0 (2018-01-01)
------------------

* First release on PyPI.


